NAME
  vtkSHYXPointExtrudeFilter
DESCRIPTION
  "Displace each point of vtkPolyData along computed point normals or a named 3-component point array; distance is constant or scaled per point by a scalar array."
GROUPS
  Meshing
DEPENDS
  VTK::FiltersCore
PRIVATE_DEPENDS
  VTK::CommonCore
  VTK::CommonDataModel
  VTK::CommonExecutionModel
